♪I keep everything you love and adore in my mind♪

3
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:30,980
♪Love feels like magic, its endless warmth wraps around you♪

4
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:37,020
♪And all my devotion. When the stars light up the sky♪

5
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,340
♪That is my answer to you♪

6
00:00:40,860 --> 00:00:47,140
♪Even if we're thousands of miles apart, my love will not waver♪

7
00:00:47,740 --> 00:00:55,060
♪Your smile creates ripples in my heart, as if you're saying "I do"♪

8
00:00:55,460 --> 00:01:01,500
♪My thoughts stretch on without end, deep beyond measure♪

9
00:01:01,780 --> 00:01:08,500
♪My love makes no sound, hidden quietly within your gaze♪

10
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:15,100
♪If we ever meet again, I'll hold you tight with all my strength♪

11
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:21,980
♪I'll run straight toward you, landing softly in your dreams♪

12
00:01:22,460 --> 00:01:26,180
