[Author: Lucky Apple Wealthy Pineapple]

16
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:40,100
[Episode 2]

17
00:01:41,740 --> 00:01:42,340
Recently,

18
00:01:42,340 --> 00:01:45,660
Zhen Group's heir, Zhen Beixing, appeared for the first time

19
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:47,980
at the press conference with the family heirloom, Flutterheart Ring,

20
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:49,260
after her return to China.

21
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:51,900
Does the sudden appearance of the long-gone Flutterheart Ring

22
00:01:51,980 --> 00:01:54,380
mean Zhen Beixing will take over Zhen Group

23
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:55,700
and become its next chairperson?

24
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:57,660
Besides, the talk of the town

25
00:01:57,900 --> 00:01:58,580
is that Ms. Zhen Beixing

26
00:01:58,580 --> 00:02:00,700
also revealed that her fiance was Mr. Gu Chen.

27
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:03,460
Can Mr. Gu Chen help Ms. Zhen Beixing

28
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:04,740
take over the Zhen Group?

29
00:02:07,340 --> 00:02:08,940
The world is indeed just a romance drama

30
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:09,900
with the domineering CEO trope.

31
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:12,340
A domineering chairperson and a handsome assistant.

32
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:14,500
A couple that only exists in novels has appeared in our world.

33
00:02:16,380 --> 00:02:19,100
No matter how excellent she is, she is someone who has just graduated.

34
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:20,460
The real decision maker of Zhen Group

35
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:23,100
is probably the Zhen family elders.

36
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:25,500
She is just a puppet.

37
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:26,700
The man is Gu Chen.

38
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:28,380
He is the assistant in name only.

39
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:30,340
In truth, he is the chairperson's fiance.

40
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:33,700
A live-in son-in-law.

41
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:34,900
Oh,

42
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:38,460
when can something like this happen to me?

43
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:40,900
Look at yourself in the mirror.

44
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:42,300
Do you think she will fancy you?

45
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:46,540
Her position isn't stable yet

46
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:48,300
and she's already appointing her own people.

47
00:02:49,090 --> 00:02:49,880
Oh,

48
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:53,260
I wonder what the old shareholders will think about this.

49
00:02:57,860 --> 00:03:01,060
It seems like you are quite the topic among the employees.

50
00:03:01,660 --> 00:03:03,060
I don't care about what they say.

51
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:05,900
I will only carry out our agreement.

52
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,560
The world is indeed just a romance drama

53
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,480
with the domineering CEO trope.

54
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,200
Gosh.

55
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,520
A domineering chairperson and a handsome assistant.

56
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,880
A couple that only exists in novels has appeared in our world.

57
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:17,320
No matter how excellent she is,

58
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,680
she is someone who has just graduated.

59
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:20,640
The real decision maker of Zhen Group is probably the Zhen family elders.

60
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,560
I've never heard about this fiance before

61
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,640
and he suddenly got appointed to a superior position.

62
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,080
Look.

63
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:27,080
That's the new chairperson, Zhen Beixing, and her fiance.

64
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,640
She's prettier in person.

65
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:31,040
She appointed one of her own as soon as she inherited the company.

66
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:32,440
He's just an assistant in name only.

67
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,080
[Gemstone Tycoon CEO, Zhen Cheng, passed away]

68
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:44,040
[Coroner's Medical Report]

69
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,120
Hello.

70
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:55,540
Sorry, Ms. Zhen.

71
00:03:55,820 --> 00:03:57,460
The last number that called your father

72
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:59,060
was from abroad and untraceable.

73
00:03:59,060 --> 00:04:00,120
Thank you.

74
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:07,740
Who was it?

75
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:10,740
Father's car crash wasn't an accident.

76
00:04:12,580 --> 00:04:14,540
It must be related to the Flutterheart Ring.

77
00:04:16,620 --> 00:04:18,220
This is your final warning.

78
00:04:18,380 --> 00:04:19,980
If you don't surrender the Flutterheart Ring,

79
00:04:20,020 --> 00:04:21,180
your daughter will be in danger.

80
00:04:21,180 --> 00:04:22,340
Who are you?

81
00:04:22,380 --> 00:04:24,980
Dad, what's wrong?

82
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:26,540
It's fine.

83
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,920
Look out!

84
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:40,340
I remember Dad was always reading a book.

85
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:41,420
I wonder

86
00:04:41,420 --> 00:04:43,660
if it contains any clues about the Flutterheart Ring.

87
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:10,020
Are you all right?

88
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:11,760
I'm fine.

89
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:27,260
What are you looking for?

90
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:28,140
Let me help you.

91
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,240
Umm...

92
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:31,140
"Genius and Crime"

93
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:43,360
["Genius and Criminal"]

94
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:47,660
Is this it?

95
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,160
Yes.

96
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:04,740
Ms. Zhen,

97
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:06,940
here's all the documents for the shareholders' meeting tomorrow.

98
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:08,220
Just leave it there.

99
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:10,140
I'll be leaving, then.

100
00:06:12,980 --> 00:06:14,540
I'm afraid we'll be facing another great challenge

101
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:17,060
in the shareholders' meeting tomorrow.

102
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:19,580
No matter what we will face tomorrow,

103
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:21,620
I will have your back.

104
00:06:24,340 --> 00:06:25,140
It's getting late.

105
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:26,060
Let me send you home.

106
00:07:00,220 --> 00:07:01,780
Dad, I miss you so much.

107
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:04,780
Tomorrow is the shareholders' meeting.

108
00:07:05,540 --> 00:07:08,380
I wonder if I can get back the company's management rights successfully.

109
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:12,340
Will she really give you the Flutterheart Ring?

110
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:16,660
- I guess. - What about the other plan?

111
00:07:16,820 --> 00:07:17,660
What's the progress?

112
00:07:17,740 --> 00:07:20,460
The chip has been installed in Zhen Beixing's phone.

113
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:22,220
Everything's according to the plan.

114
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:24,420
Are you sure it's her?

115
00:07:24,660 --> 00:07:25,540
I don't know.

116
00:07:27,660 --> 00:07:28,580
But I think

117
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:33,660
I'll know the truth if I stay beside her.

118
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:37,820
All right. This is more complicated than we imagined.

119
00:07:38,660 --> 00:07:40,540
Gu Chen, stay safe.

120
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:42,940
The key to this operation

121
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:44,340
is to not attract other people's attention.

122
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,740
Especially those wily old foxes in the Zhen family.

123
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:48,980
I understand.

124
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:58,060
Why isn't Zhen Beixing here yet?

125
00:07:58,140 --> 00:07:59,620
She's already late when she just took over the company.

126
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:01,940
Is she looking down on us?

127
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:02,820
Everyone, look.

128
00:08:03,540 --> 00:08:07,060
This is Zhen Beixing's sense of responsibility and professionalism.

129
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:09,180
She can't even do the bare minimum and be punctual.

130
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:12,340
How can she lead the Zhen Group?

131
00:08:21,780 --> 00:08:22,580
Zhen Beixing,

132
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:24,620
play nice now.

133
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:26,780
Otherwise, I won't be nice to you.

134
00:08:27,740 --> 00:08:28,660
Who do you work for?

135
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:29,460
This is none of your business.

136
00:08:29,540 --> 00:08:31,780
[Shares Transfer Agreement]
If you don't surrender your shares,

137
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:34,020
you will die today.

138
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:35,180
If I hand over the shares,

139
00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:36,940
will you let me go?

140
00:08:38,580 --> 00:08:40,180
Why should I believe in you?

141
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:42,180
Ask your employer to negotiate with me.

142
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:44,980
Otherwise, I won't sign it.

143
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:49,180
Mr. Zhen Quan

144
00:08:49,220 --> 00:08:51,180
has always been a pillar of the company.

145
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:52,860
Be it in terms of the company's stability

146
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:54,980
or future development,

147
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:58,420
Zhen Quan is the best candidate to be the chairperson.

148
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:03,060
Perhaps Zhen Beixing realizes her incapability for this role,

149
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:04,260
so she chose to be absent.

150
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:05,820
In comparison,

151
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:08,420
Mr. Zhen Quan is experienced

152
00:09:08,940 --> 00:09:10,140
and astute.

153
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:12,860
I'm sure he can lead the group to greater heights.

154
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:16,940
He is the leader that our group needs.

155
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,160
Yes.

156
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:34,020
Zhen Beixing just returned to the country

157
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:36,260
and there has already been a scandal involving her fiance.

158
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:37,820
Her actions

159
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:40,020
have tarnished the company's image greatly.

160
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:41,540
Moreover, she's late to the meeting.

161
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:43,180
Her behavior

162
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:45,260
does not inspire public confidence

163
00:09:45,420 --> 00:09:47,420
with regard to entrusting her with the future

164
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,740
of the group.

165
00:10:03,140 --> 00:10:04,140
Stop.

166
00:10:04,380 --> 00:10:05,940
The meeting hasn't begun yet.

167
00:10:05,940 --> 00:10:06,980
If you make a decision now,

168
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:08,980
it's very unfair.

169
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:10,140
No one will accept it.

170
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:13,180
There's half an hour until the meeting begins.

171
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:16,020
When the time comes, and Zhen Beixing isn't here yet,

172
00:10:16,780 --> 00:10:18,460
she will be deemed

173
00:10:18,540 --> 00:10:21,580
to have given up her authority according to the family constitution.

174
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:23,060
Before this,

175
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:25,180
no further comments are allowed.

176
00:10:31,820 --> 00:10:32,620
Hello, Lin Mo.

177
00:10:33,820 --> 00:10:34,860
Zhen Beixing isn't home

178
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:36,180
or at the shareholders' meeting.

179
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:37,740
Trace her phone immediately

180
00:10:37,740 --> 00:10:38,540
and see where she's at.

181
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,480
[No signal]

182
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,200
Oh, no.

183
00:10:43,460 --> 00:10:44,540
The signal has been jammed.

184
00:10:44,540 --> 00:10:46,540
Urgh! I shouldn't have left her at home alone.

185
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:49,180
I can only track the last known location of the signal.

186
00:10:49,180 --> 00:10:49,780
[Western Suburb Warehouse]

187
00:10:49,780 --> 00:10:53,260
It's near an abandoned warehouse in the Western Suburb.

188
00:10:57,740 --> 00:11:00,860
Zhen Beixing, nothing must happen to you. Wait for me.

189
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:21,780
Got it, Boss.

190
00:11:27,510 --> 00:11:28,320
Ah!

191
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:34,060
You're still trying to escape when you're just a cripple.

192
00:11:34,340 --> 00:11:36,340
You deserve to be punished!

193
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:46,380
Who are you?

194
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:02,380
Gu Chen.

195
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:21,580
You are hurt.

196
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:23,140
Let's get your wounds treated at the hospital first.

197
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:24,340
It's too late.

198
00:12:24,460 --> 00:12:25,740
I must attend the shareholders' meeting.

199
00:12:25,820 --> 00:12:27,140
I can't be absent now.

200
00:12:27,260 --> 00:12:28,980
- Can you hold on? - Yes.

201
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:32,780
Hey, we won't make it!

202
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:36,180
We will make it.

203
00:13:13,660 --> 00:13:14,740
We've been waiting until nighttime.

204
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:16,540
Let's not wait for Zhen Beixing anymore

205
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:18,060
and begin the shareholders' meeting.

206
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:19,380
According to the company's rule,

207
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:22,620
Zhen Beixing's absence means she is giving up her authority.

208
00:13:23,580 --> 00:13:25,340
Sir, make the announcement.

209
00:13:25,620 --> 00:13:28,340
Yes, my time is precious.

210
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:29,620
Let's begin the meeting.

211
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:49,340
You can't go inside!

212
00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:51,800
Ah!

213
00:14:25,290 --> 00:14:32,730
♪The hazy streets rewind, bidding farewell to every heartbroken visitor♪

214
00:14:33,210 --> 00:14:40,410
♪Parting flowers wither and fall, their lingering fragrance fades away♪

215
00:14:41,170 --> 00:14:48,370
♪Your figure is swallowed by the crowd, as if you never stood by my side♪

216
00:14:49,290 --> 00:14:57,930
♪The once moving vows vanish with the passing of time, who remembers them?♪

217
00:14:59,010 --> 00:15:03,420
♪It's hard to define what I've truly possessed until now♪

218
00:15:04,170 --> 00:15:08,410
♪Was it you or just memories? Snow melts, winter passes♪

219
00:15:09,090 --> 00:15:14,410
♪Everything is like our fleeting encounter, how can one let it go?♪

220
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:19,250
♪It's hard to define what I've truly possessed until now♪

221
00:15:19,890 --> 00:15:24,530
♪Was it love or regret? Amid the river of time and sea of people♪

222
00:15:25,130 --> 00:15:33,130
♪You and I embrace only for a moment before we part unwillingly♪
